        *   Change `aesop` to `simp_all`.
    *   In the `case cons C σ IH` part:
        *   Change `specialize IH (⁻o) _ (⁻o') (by simp at same_len; assumption) equ.1` to `specialize IH (⁻o) _ (⁻o') (by simp at same_len; assumption) equ`.
